code: @Override public boolean process(Exchange exchange, AsyncCallback callback) {     getCurrentSagaCoordinator(exchange).whenComplete((coordinator, ex) -> ifNotException(ex, exchange, callback, () -> {         if (coordinator != null) {             exchange.setException(new CamelExchangeException("Route cannot handle exchanges that are joining a saga", exchange)).             callback.done(false).         } else {             super.process(exchange, doneSync -> callback.done(false)).         }     })).     return false. }
